nnemi et sont pris dans une embuscade tendue par un groupe de criminels."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"边境奇袭","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"一场人质营救行动带来了新的敌人，格雷罗上尉和他的精英士兵们必须应对残忍犯罪团伙的埋伏。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Contra-Ataque","runtime":85,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/br/title/81936018","overview":"Uma missão de resgate faz surgir um novo inimigo, levando o capitão Guerrero e seus soldados de elite a enfrentar uma emboscada de um grupo criminoso."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Ellentámadás","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hu/title/81936018","overview":"Amikor egy túszmentés során Guerrero százados újabb ellenséget szerez, elit katonáinak szembe kell nézniük egy könyörtelen bűnbanda bosszújával."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Kontratak","runtime":85,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/pl/title/81936018","overview":"Misja odbicia zakładników przysparza nowego wroga kapitanowi Guerrero i jego elitarnemu oddziałowi, i stawia ich na celowniku grupy przestępczej."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Karşı Atak","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tr/title/81936018","overview":"Bir rehine kurtarma operasyonunun ardından yeni bir düşman edinen Yüzbaşı Guerrero ve onun elit askerleri, bir suç örgütünün saldırısıyla karşı karşıya kalır."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Der Gegenangriff","runtime":84,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/de/title/81936018","overview":"Als sich Capitán Guerrero und seine Elite-Soldaten bei der Rettung zweier Geiseln einen neuen Feind machen, geraten sie in den Hinterhalt einer kriminellen Gruppierung."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Contraatac","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ro/title/81936018","overview":"O misiune de salvare a ostaticilor creează un nou dușman, iar căpitanul Guerrero și soldații săi de elită trebuie să iasă din ambuscada unei grupări criminale."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/es/title/81936018","overview":"En una misión de rescate de rehenes, el capitán Guerrero y sus soldados de élite sufren una emboscada de un despiadado cártel de la droga."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"מכת נגד","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/il/title/81936018","overview":"משימה לחילוץ בני ערובה מולידה אויב חדש. קפטן גררו וחייליו המובחרים יצטרכו להתמודד עם מארב של ארגון פשע."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Phản công","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/vn/title/81936018","overview":"Khi nhiệm vụ giải cứu con tin dẫn đến thêm kẻ thù mới, đại úy Guerrero cùng đội lính tinh nhuệ phải đối mặt với cuộc phục kích của một nhóm tội phạm."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Protiútok","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/cz/title/81936018","overview":"Při záchraně rukojmích si kapitán Guerrero a jeho elitní vojáci udělají nového nepřítele, a stanou se proto terčem útoku ze strany brutálního gangu."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/mx/title/81936018","overview":"Tras rescatar a dos rehenes y hacerse de un nuevo enemigo, el capitán Guerrero y su escuadrón de élite se enfrentan a la emboscada de un grupo criminal."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Контрудар","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ua/title/81936018","overview":"Коли місія з порятунку заручників призводить до виникнення нового ворога, на капітана Ґерреро і його елітний підрозділ чекає засідка злочинного угрупування."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/nl/title/81936018","overview":"Nadat kapitein Guerrero tijdens een reddingsmissie een nieuwe vijand heeft gemaakt, loopt hij met zijn elitesoldaten in de hinderlaag van een criminele organisatie."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"カウンターアタック","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/jp/title/81936018","overview":"人質救出作戦で新たな敵を作ったゲレロ大尉。彼とその精鋭の部下たちを待ち受けていたのは、犯罪者グループによる急襲だった。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"ضد حمله","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"در یک سفر به مرز آمریکا و مکزیک، گروهی متشکل از پنج دوست توسط گروهی از خلافکاران حرفه‌ای مورد تعقیب قرار می‌گیرند. اما این قاتلان حرفه‌ای نمی‌دانند که این پنج دوست، اعضای نیروهای ویژه نظامی مکزیک هستند. اینبار، اوضاع آن‌طور که خلافکاران برنامه‌ریزی کرده‌اند، پیش نمی‌رود و ..."},"name":"فارسی","iso_639_1":"fa","iso_3166_1":"IR","english_name":"Persian"},{"data":{"title":"Контра Атака","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Когато мисия за спасяване на заложници създава нов враг, капитан Гереро и неговият елитен отряд трябва да се изправят срещу засада, устроена от безмилостен наркокартел."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"邊境奇襲","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/tw/title/81936018","overview":"營救人質任務招來新敵人，格雷洛上尉和他率領的精銳士兵必須面對犯罪集團的伏擊。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Il contrattacco","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/it/title/81936018","overview":"Dopo essersi fatti un nuovo nemico per salvare degli ostaggi, il capitano Guerrero e i suoi soldati scelti cadono nell'imboscata orchestrata da un gruppo criminale."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Αντεπίθεση","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/gr/title/81936018","overview":"Όταν αποκτά έναν νέο εχθρό μετά από μια αποστολή διάσωσης ομήρων, ο λοχαγός Γκερέρο κι οι στρατιώτες του πέφτουν στην ενέδρα μιας αδίστακτης εγκληματικής ομάδας."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Ko jim reševalna akcija talcev ustvari novega sovražnika, se kapitan Guerrero s svojimi elitnimi vojaki znajde v navzkrižnem ognju neusmiljenega narkokartela."},"name":"Slovenščina","iso_639_1":"sl","iso_3166_1":"SI","english_name":"Slovenian"},{"data":{"title":"هجوم مضاد","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ae/title/81936018","overview":"بعد أن تتسبب مهمة إنقاذ رهينتين في ظهور عدو جديد، يجد النقيب \"غيريرو\" وجنوده من النخبة أنفسهم في مواجهة كمين خطير نصبته جماعة من المجرمين."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"AE","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"هجوم مضاد","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sa/title/81936018","overview":"بعد أن تتسبب مهمة إنقاذ رهينتين في ظهور عدو جديد، يجد النقيب \"غيريرو\" وجنوده من النخبة أنفسهم في مواجهة كمين خطير نصبته جماعة من المجرمين."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"邊境奇襲","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hk/title/81936018","overview":"營救人質任務招來新敵人，格雷洛上尉和他率領的精銳士兵必須面對犯罪集團的伏擊。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"边境奇袭","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/sg-zh/title/81936018","overview":"一场人质营救行动带来了新的敌人，格雷罗上尉和他的精英士兵们必须应对残忍犯罪团伙的埋伏。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"SG","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Protuudar","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/hr/title/81936018","overview":"Nakon što tijekom misije spašavanja steknu novog neprijatelja, satnik Guerrero i njegova elitna postrojba nađu se u zasjedi kriminalne skupine."},"name":"Hrvatski","iso_639_1":"hr","iso_3166_1":"HR","english_name":"Croatian"},{"data":{"title":"Modangreb","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/dk/title/81936018","overview":"Da en gidselredningsmission skaber en ny fjende, må Guerrero og hans elitesoldater afværge et bagholdsangreb fra en kriminel gruppe."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Vastaisku","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/fi/title/81936018","overview":"Panttivankien pelastusoperaatiosta syntyy uusi vihollinen, ja kapteeni Guerrero eliittisotilaineen joutuu rikollisjoukkion väijytykseen."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Contre-attaque","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ca-fr/title/81936018","overview":"Quand une mission de sauvetage d'otages leur crée un nouvel ennemi, le capitaine Guerrero et ses soldats d'élite subissent les foudres d'un groupe criminel."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Counterattack","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/in-hi/title/81936018","overview":""},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"Counterattack","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/id/title/81936018","overview":"Saat misi penyelamatan sandera malah menciptakan musuh baru, Kapten Guerrero dan para prajurit elitenya harus menghadapi penyergapan oleh sebuah kelompok kriminal."},"name":"Bahasa indonesia","iso_639_1":"id","iso_3166_1":"ID","english_name":"Indonesian"},{"data":{"title":"Counterattack","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/my/title/81936018","overview":"Apabila misi menyelamat tebusan mencipta musuh baharu, Kapten Guerrero dan askar elitnya harus berdepan serangan hendap oleh sekumpulan penjenayah."},"name":"Bahasa melayu","iso_639_1":"ms","iso_3166_1":"MY","english_name":"Malay"},{"data":{"title":"Motangrep","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/no/title/81936018","overview":"En gisselredningsaksjon skaper en ny fiende, og kaptein Guerrero og elitesoldatene hans må motstå et bakholdsangrep fra en kriminell organisasjon."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"Contra-Ataque","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/pt/title/81936018","overview":"Quando uma missão de salvamento lhes granjeia um novo inimigo, o capitão Guerrero e os seus soldados de elite enfrentam uma emboscada por parte de um grupo criminoso."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Контратака","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ru/title/81936018","overview":"Когда в ходе операции по освобождению заложников появляется новый враг, капитан Герреро и его элитные солдаты сталкиваются с засадой, устроенной преступной группировкой."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/se/title/81936018","overview":"När ett fritagningsuppdrag ger dem en ny fiende blir Guerrero och hans elitsoldater angripna av en hänsynslös kriminell organisation."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Counterattack","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.netflix.com/ph/title/81936018","overview":"Nang magkaroon ng bagong kaaway si Kapitan Guerrero at mga elite niyang sundalo dahil sa pagsagip sa isang hostage, isang grupo ng mga kriminal ang nang-ambush sa kanila."},"name":"","iso_639_1":"tl","iso_3166_1":"PH","english_name":"Tagalog"},{"data":{"title":"კონტრშეტევა","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"ქართული","iso_639_1":"ka","iso_3166_1":"GE","english_name":"Georgian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":1302151,"adult":false,"title":"Mesa de regalos","video":false,"overview":"Nicolás and Antonia are two inseparable friends who are far from the emotional and professional stability that all their acquaintances have achieved. After attending countless weddings, they come up with a plan as bold as it is ingenious: to fund their dreams by organizing their own fake wedding! They announce their \"secret love,\" plan a big celebration, and at the crucial moment, Antonia is to leave Nicolás standing at the altar. Confident that the scandal will discourage guests from claiming their gifts, they plan to split the loot. However, unexpected feelings begin to arise, which could complicate their brilliant plan.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.949,"vote_count":103,"poster_path":"/xDHlLybirflJFlvPFVHhcTKAZQ2.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-16","vote_average":8.563,"backdrop_path":"/k50zwn8Gs4f999ezuVAL2WXLv5x.jpg","original_title":"Mesa de regalos","original_language":"es"},{"id":1230208,"adult":false,"title":"Squad 36","video":false,"overview":"Forced out of his elite unit, a troubled cop launches his own rogue investigation when mysterious killings claim the lives of his former colleagues.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8156,"vote_count":1