t to discover that Japan has disappeared, and a giant island - Hinomoto - is now in the sky over Gotham City.  At the top sit the Yakuza, a group of superpowered individuals who reign without honor or humanity and look suspiciously like the Justice League. Now, it’s up to Batman and his allies to save Gotham!","genre_ids":[16,28,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.8097,"vote_count":219,"poster_path":"/sVVT6GYFErVv0Lcc9NvqCu0iOxO.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-17","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/e807jDKiFcntZS32ze88X6I96OD.jpg","original_title":"ニンジャバットマン対ヤクザリーグ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1126166,"adult":false,"title":"Flight Risk","video":false,"overview":"A pilot transports a U.S. Marshal accompanying a government witness to a trial in New York. As they cross the Alaskan wilderness, tensions soar and trust is tested, as not everyone on board is who they seem.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.4295,"vote_count":1103,"poster_path":"/q0bCG4NX32iIEsRFZqRtuvzNCyZ.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-22","vote_average":5.945,"backdrop_path":"/hwlyY7LJdEFbCPaGNXiskKKmJ5X.jpg","original_title":"Flight Risk","original_language":"en"},{"id":1276073,"adult":false,"title":"Bullet Train Explosion","video":false,"overview":"When panic erupts on a Tokyo-bound bullet train that will explode if it slows below 100 kph, authorities race against time to save everyone on board.","genre_ids":[28,53,80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.7233,"vote_count":292,"poster_path":"/jmzxlDBwgvRbpPJzNQwizyn9UEn.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-23","vote_average":6.851,"backdrop_path":"/zHP9pMtYuMZBluNZNBP9i5fX2US.jpg","original_title":"新幹線大爆破","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1450599,"adult":false,"title":"K.O.","video":false,"overview":"A former fighter must find the missing son of an opponent he accidentally killed years ago, taking on a brutally violent crime gang in Marseille.","genre_ids":[28,18,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.3888,"vote_count":259,"poster