ect puts new superweapons in dangerous hands, John Henry Irons becomes Steel. Wearing body armor, wielding a fearsome electrohammer and riding a gadget-packed motorcycle, he's ready to wage war... if he can fix the untimely glitches in his untested gear.","genre_ids":[878,28,80,14],"popularity":2.4995,"vote_count":272,"poster_path":"/ufA7d5LT2rGj58KaZErPhcMkJ4U.jpg","release_date":"1997-08-15","vote_average":4.283,"backdrop_path":"/61Wj1C1hrOyu6mAHARS8J5ShOzq.jpg","original_title":"Steel","original_language":"en"},{"id":8814,"adult":false,"title":"Doom","video":false,"overview":"A team of space marines known as the Rapid Response Tactical Squad, led by Sarge, is sent to a science facility on Mars after somebody reports a security breach. There, they learn that the alert came after a test subject, a mass murderer purposefully injected with alien DNA, broke free and began killing people. Dr. Grimm, who is related to team member Reaper, informs them all that the chromosome can mutate humans into monsters -- and is highly infectious.","genre_ids":[28,27,878],"popularity":4.2513,"vote_count":2383,"poster_path":"/y50lH061yWOvEstoZRn7lYs0huk.jpg","release_date":"2005-10-20","vote_average":5.181,"backdrop_path":"/9EpgaLS44zlXoTSAOhGiJmkIA4B.jpg","original_title":"Doom","original_language":"en"},{"id":9086,"adult":false,"title":"Young Guns II","video":false,"overview":"Three of the original five \"young guns\" — Billy the Kid, Jose Chavez y Chavez, and Doc Scurlock — return in Young Guns, Part 2, which is the story of Billy the Kid and his race to safety in Old Mexico while being trailed by a group of government agents led by Pat Garrett.","genre_ids":[37,12],"popularity":1.5669,"vote_count":579,"poster_path":"/7kMjla98srGHlFzAEmoGRcr6GN1.jpg","release_date":"1990-08-01","vote_average":6.503,"backdrop_path":"/sQNPWOTzl5kkZTW5ogSu0uSnreB.jpg","original_title":"Young Guns II","original_language":"en"},{"id":9093,"adult":false,"title":"The Four Feathers","video":false,"overview":"A young British officer resigns his post when he learns of his regiment's plan to ship out to the Sudan for the conflict with the Mahdi. His friends and fiancée send him four white feathers as symbols of what they view as his cowardice. To redeem his honor, he disguises himself as an Arab and secretly saves their lives.","genre_ids":[28,12,18,10749,10752],"popularity":1.9286,"vote_count":580,"poster_path":"/bfmpeRr9LTXzBC2dpC89FE5uavK.jpg","release_date":"2002-09-08","vote_average":6.631,"backdrop_path":"/2IojDzEWedVbre8KZhZPMoP5az4.jpg","original_title":"The Four Feathers","original_language":"en"},{"id":9367,"adult":false,"title":"El Mariachi","video":false,"overview":"El Mariachi just wants to play his guitar and carry on the family tradition. Unfortunately, the town he tries to find work in has another visitor, a killer who carries his guns in a guitar case. The drug lord and his henchmen mistake el Mariachi for the killer, Azul, and chase him around town trying to kill him and get his guitar case.","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"popularity":2.5583,"vote_count":1250,"poster_path":"/zRh7K4SV1xQ419m8gzGITak51vc.jpg","release_date":"1993-02-22","vote_average":6.745,"backdrop_path":"/zERY2aaCrLExpR6NQ1ceIs0WG8S.jpg","original_title":"El Mariachi","original_language":"es"},{"id":471604,"adult":false,"title":"Join the Marines","video":false,"overview":"New York City cop Phil Donlon leaves the force to join the U.S. Olympic team. When he falls for a Marine colonel's daughter he gets kicked off the team. Joining the Marines to win the Colonel's approval many adventures follow.","genre_ids":[28],"popularity":0.2007,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/kjhNJ5kUFAdUFi5aZemuQO4c6w5.jpg","release_date":"1937-01-25","vote_average":3,"backdrop_path":"/lyw4F0MrQgkYmp6HmhElaSzNXqT.jpg","original_title":"Join the Marines","original_language":"en"},{"id":9208,"adult":false,"title":"Broken Arrow","video":false,"overview":"When rogue stealth-fighter pilot Vic Deakins deliberately drops off the radar while on maneuvers, the Air Force ends up with two stolen nuclear warheads -- and Deakins's co-pilot, Riley Hale, is the military's only hope for getting them back. Traversing the deserted canyons of Utah, Hale teams with park ranger Terry Carmichael to put Deakins back in his box.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":2.6629,"vote_count":1629,"poster_path":"/iBPMwYYJFvdCBkXrwV75peo5Lz2.jpg","release_date":"1996-02-09","vote_average":6.06,"backdrop_path":"/446lXnrT0vSIkeClW8bCN8KrnxN.jpg","original_title":"Broken Arrow","original_language":"en"},{"id":9509,"adult":false,"title":"Man on Fire","video":false,"overview":"Jaded ex-CIA operative John Creasy reluctantly accepts a job as the bodyguard for a 10-year-old girl in Mexico City. They clash at first, but eventually bond, and when she's kidnapped he's consumed by fury and will stop at nothing to save her life.","genre_ids":[28,18,53],"popularity":6.9493,"vote_count":5534,"poster_path":"/grCGLCcTHv9TChibzOwzUpykcjB.jpg","release_date":"2004-04-23","vote_average":7.457,"backdrop_path":"/6c7j7MQCczzNVvcrNEiXbs8Kt2p.jpg","original_title":"Man on Fire","original_language":"en"},{"id":9425,"adult":false,"title":"Soldier","video":false,"overview":"Sergeant Todd is a veteran soldier for an elite group of the armed forces. After being defeated by a new breed of genetically engineered soldiers, he is dumped on a waste planet and left for dead. He soon interacts with a group of crash survivors who lead out a peaceful existence. The peace is broken as the new soldiers land on the planet to eliminate the colony, which Sergeant Todd must defend.","genre_ids":[878,28,18],"popularity":2.1657,"vote_count":911,"poster_path":"/rYy5m4nnjdlvB6dyGkP9ELZbUZz.jpg","release_date":"1998-10-23","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/eYrjffVvcc0MEgy9RcquvWyBGtQ.jpg","original_title":"Soldier","original_language":"en"},{"id":170,"adult":false,"title":"28 Days Later","video":false,"overview":"Twenty-eight days after a killer virus was accidentally unleashed from a British research facility, a small group of London survivors are caught in a desperate struggle to protect themselves from the infected. Carried by animals and humans, the virus turns those it infects into homicidal maniacs -- and it's absolutely impossible to contain.","genre_ids":[27,53,878],"popularity":17.7462,"vote_count":8256,"poster_path":"/sQckQRt17VaWbo39GIu0TMOiszq.jpg","release_date":"2002-10-31","vote_average":7.236,"backdrop_path":"/aJFwk1clMal1prxAvKAgHxKPAf.jpg","original_title":"28 Days Later","original_language":"en"},{"id":18,"adult":false,"title":"The Fifth Element","video":false,"overview":"In 2257, a taxi driver is unintentionally given the task of saving a young girl who is part of the key that will ensure the survival of humanity.","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"popularity":12.1549,"vote_count":11467,"poster_path":"/fPtlCO1yQtnoLHOwKtWz7db6RGU.jpg","release_date":"1997-05-02","vote_average":7.563,"backdrop_path":"/bx1W729hyWQqNQoiq9LsX30FBf.jpg","original_title":"Le Cinquième Élément","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1642,"adult":false,"title":"The Net","video":false,"overview":"Angela Bennett is a freelance computer systems analyst who tracks down software viruses. At night she hooks up to the internet and chats to others 'surfing the net'. While de-bugging a new high-tech game for a cyber friend, she comes across a top secret program and becomes the target of a mysterious organization who will stop at nothing to erase her identity and her existence, in order to protect the project.","genre_ids":[80,18,9648,53,28],"popularity":2.23,"vote_count":1480,"poster_path":"/dtupntUFMD5iXBo8HLfALt2ET4R.jpg","release_date":"1995-07-28","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/lmjReP9aoEZFFyqDP1JP4F0Ohsf.jpg","original_title":"The Net","original_language":"en"},{"id":1656,"adult":false,"title":"The Legend of Zorro","video":false,"overview":"Despite trying to keep his swashbuckling to a minimum, a threat to California's pending statehood causes the adventure-loving Don Alejandro de la Vega and his wife, Elena, to take action.","genre_ids":[28,12,37],"popularity":2.8594,"vote_count":3042,"poster_path":"/duZDsuIA2uX93Vujtm89oHeTFqE.jpg","release_date":"2005-10-24","vote_average":6.12,"backdrop_path":"/zrqHFQrF2HngVcEFRtW6sf1nIBD.jpg","original_title":"The Legend of Zorro","original_language":"en"},{"id":1724,"adult":false,"title":"The Incredible Hulk","video":false,"overview":"Scientist Bruce Banner scours the planet for an antidote to the unbridled force of rage within him: the Hulk. But when the military masterminds who dream of exploiting his powers force him back to civilization, he finds himself coming face to face with a new, deadly foe.","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"popularity":10.6929,"vote_count":12500,"poster_path":"/gKzYx79y0AQTL4UAk1cBQJ3nvrm.jpg","release_date":"2008-06-12","vote_average":6.231,"backdrop_path":"/jPu8yiadqgzwFPGKJmGo637ASVP.jpg","original_title":"The Incredible Hulk","original_language":"en"},{"id":1969,"adult":false,"title":"Bandidas","video":false,"overview":"When a ruthless robber baron takes away everything they cherish, a rough-and-tumble, idealistic peasant and a sophisticated heiress embark on a quest for justice, vengeance…and a few good heists.","genre_ids":[28,35,37,80],"popularity":2.4527,"vote_count":1157,"poster_path":"/31wgXG6OxDaXbp5IzyNoUJdVS5e.jpg","release_date":"2006-01-18","vote_average":6.027,"backdrop_path":"/vmDpLofmDgDx3KXTNzRc6dYROim.jpg","original_title":"Bandidas","original_language":"en"},{"id":1979,"adult":false,"title":"Fantastic Four: Rise of the Silver Surfer","video":false,"overview":"The Fantastic Four return to the big screen as a new and all powerful enemy threatens the Earth. The seemingly unstoppable 'Silver Surfer', but all is not what it seems and there are old and new enemies that pose a greater threat than the intrepid superheroes realize.","genre_ids":[878,12,28],"popularity":6.028,"vote_count":8294,"poster_path":"/1rxTraSO45jbvTrCeSvJ6RmOu1